t dessen, was lange Zeit als »Militarismus« kritisiert worden ist, verändert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aGewalt. 4aKonfliktforschung. 4aKrieg. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitische Soziologie. 4aSoziologie. 4aTerrorismus. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aConflict Studies.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Sociology.  aSociology.  aViolence.1 aWarburg, Jens, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW0 cprintz978389942245040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839402450?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839402450423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839402450/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009